{"tid":1827729,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"渣哥茶記黃色主色","createTime":"2020-01-17T07:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T07:39:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2c11ee190629a21e82bdf8d6408326c293a489","tid":1827729,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:26:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200117/SY7ITXGFVEOXULSSMVQR2CYLJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200117%2FSY7ITXGFVEOXULSSMVQR2CYLJM%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyh4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=2acd4788\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200117%2FSY7ITXGFVEOXULSSMVQR2CYLJM%2F&h=e293207c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200117/SY7ITXGFVEOXULSSMVQR2CYLJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n渣哥茶記黃色主色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200117/large/1579183067_1518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200117%2Flarge%2F1579183067_1518.jpg&h=06b4408b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渣哥在店舖中不時與工作人員討論裝修的進度。<br />\n<br />\n譚小環2014年獲老公蔡強榮（渣哥）打本在銅鑼灣開小食店「渣哥一九九六」，幾年間店舖一變三，渣哥日前公佈下月1日將在九龍灣開「大渣哥茶記」。大渣哥的裝修如火如荼，日前渣哥到新店視察裝修，雖未見小環同行，不過渣哥都親力親為，不時進出店舖打點，並與現場的工作人員討論，當他獲悉商場洗手間被沙泥淤塞了，也有跟友人去了解。店外圍上黃綠色圍板，上面寫了「不反胃通知書，申請中&hellip;&hellip;。」店內佈置以黃色為主，果然是「黃店」。渣哥逗留了半小時便上一部七人車離開，隱約見到戴了口罩的小環在車內等候。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》昨日致電渣哥，他表示裝修進度理想，農曆新年後便開店：「我哋有要求，想整靚啲，等大家嚟坐得舒服啲。」據知大渣哥斥資逾七位數字，雖然經濟轉差，但他表示仍有信心，最緊要食物及服務質素。<br />\n<br />\n採訪、攝影：梁繼光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200117/large/1579183066_be67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200117%2Flarge%2F1579183066_be67.jpg&h=3e2bdb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚小環逗留在車上等候渣哥。"},{"pid":"1c359c0638bb862ff1ae848752b5668573d76182","tid":1827729,"uid":8918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"逆市開張<br />\n主題鮮明 到時日日排長龍<br />\n絕對大巴大巴打落啲官媒度"}]}